Marseilles, Frankfurt Hahn Airports Face EU State Aid Probes

-- B y   A o i f e   W h i t e
-- 
2011-07-13T09:45:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/marseilles-frankfurt-hahn-airports-face-eu-state-aid-probes.html
European Union regulators will
investigate government support for  France ’s Marseilles airport
and  Germany ’s Frankfurt Hahn airport.  The European Commission will also examine Ireland’s tax on
air passengers that imposed a higher fee on foreign flights
until March, it said in an e-mailed statement from Brussels
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aoife White in Brussels at 
 awhite62@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anthony Aarons at   aaarons@bloomberg.net . 